\fs24 \cf0 Core idea:
\f0\b0  A public, permanent, searchable archive of fan-captured media \'97 organized by entity (artist/team/event brand) 
\f4 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  specific occurrence (date/show/game). Think of it as 
\f2\b the fan's version of Getty Images
\f0\b0  \'97 but free, crowdsourced, and built around the experience of being there.\
