\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 3. Tech stack\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Frontend\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 React or Next.js \'97 you need SSR for SEO. These event pages need to rank on Google ("Cardi B concert photos 2025") and server-side rendering is non-negotiable for that. Next.js with App Router is the current standard choice.\
Mobile app: React Native shares a ton of logic with the web codebase. The mobile app is important for the upload experience \'97 you want a native camera roll integration, not a web upload picker.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf0 Media storage\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 This is the single most consequential technical decision. Cloudflare R2 at $0.015/GB stored with free egress is 60-80% cheaper than S3+CloudFront at scale, and the delivery cost of S3+CloudFront is roughly 18x the storage cost \'97 so egress is where you'd get killed if you chose wrong. R2 is the right call for a media-heavy platform. {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://leanopstech.com/blog/media-storage-serverless-cost-comparison-2026/"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 \ul \ulc6 \strokec6 LeanOps TechnologiesLeanOps Technologies}}\
For video specifically: Mux charges ~$0.007/min delivered but includes encoding, adaptive bitrate streaming, and analytics \'97 worthwhile for a platform where video quality matters. You get HLS adaptive streaming, thumbnail generation, and a player that works everywhere. {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://leanopstech.com/blog/media-storage-serverless-cost-comparison-2026/"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 \ul \ulc6 \strokec6 LeanOps Technologies}}\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf0 Search\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 Algolia or Typesense for event/entity search. You need instant, typo-tolerant search ("Beyonc\'e9" vs "Beyonce", "Phillies" vs "Phils"). Algolia has the better product; Typesense is cheaper and self-hostable. Either integrates well with a Next.js stack.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

