\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Archive-forward
\f0\b0 : Fanarchive, Crowdview, Showvault \'97 emphasizes permanence and the historical value\
\ls11\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Fan-forward
\f0\b0 : Fanframe, Crowdshot, Showside \'97 emphasizes community and perspective\
\ls11\ilvl0
\f2\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Experience-forward
\f0\b0 : Wewere.there, Seatview, Livefeed \'97 emphasizes "I was there"\
