\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Great question \'97 this is one of the most technically interesting and highest-value features on the platform. Let me break down exactly how it works end to end.\
There are two paths to get a video linked to a song: 
\f2\b uploader tags it manually
\f0\b0 , or 
\f2\b the platform tags it automatically
\f0\b0 . In practice you want both running in parallel, with auto-tagging filling in the gaps that manual tagging misses.\
