\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Upload starts in the background the moment they confirm \'97 they can close the browser and it still completes\
\ls21\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
