\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The visual aesthetic should feel cinematic and fan-authentic \'97 dark backgrounds, warm accent colors, content-forward. It should feel like being in the venue, not like a database browser. Key principles:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls53\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Video is the hero content type \'97 lead with it everywhere\
\ls53\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Dark theme throughout \'97 both because it suits the concert/sports context and because it makes media thumbnails pop\
\ls53\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The entity page hero should feel like a movie poster for the artist \'97 immersive, not corporate\
\ls53\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Filter pills and navigation should feel lightweight and fast \'97 this is a browsing experience, not a research tool\
\ls53\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Mobile experience is primary \'97 most users will arrive on a phone, either uploading after a show or browsing from their couch\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The mockup we designed together (visible in prior conversation) shows: dark cinematic hero with video thumbnails on the right, fan highlights grid with mood filters, most filmed songs with relative bars, recent shows cards, and a collapsed archive section at the bottom.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

